   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3170_0063"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168934">IX. Frankga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 1</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3170_0062"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb141802">Der Weisse Knott</rs></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3170_0062"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb91918">Trafoi</rs></hi>, <date when="1900-09-02">2. September</date>.</dateline><salute rend="left">Mein lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Ich danke für Dein Telegramm. Komme voraus<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ichtlich <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02929-1"/><date when="1900-09-04">Dien<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date> oder <date when="1900-09-05">Mittwoch</date>
               nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02929-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs> hielt sich jedenfalls vom <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1900-09-06" subtype="date-only"/> bis zum <ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L02930" subtype="date-only"/> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs> auf.</note> und wäre Dir<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr dankbar, wenn
               Du mir im <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb585">Hotel Hammerand</rs></hi> ein Zimmer be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tellen wollte<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t. Herzl. Gruß. <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></p></div>
      </body>
